    "This requires continuous learning capabilities, where models can update their policies based on real-time feedback without losing performance stability.",
    "However, balancing adaptability with stability is a non-trivial challenge; overly frequent updates can lead to overfitting or erratic behavior.Another critical aspect is the need for transfer learning capabilities, where models trained in one educational setting can be adapted to others with minimal retraining.",
